

=Description=

"Startup for online auction system (i.e. mini-Ebay) where all trading is done in virtual credits. 
Company give away credits to users for starting an account and more for completing little tasks (like 
listing an item or completing one's profile). Appears to have a fairly large number of active users. 
Virtual credits  can be exchanged out of the system by listing gift cards, putting the credit exchange rate at  approximately 1000 credits to one dollar."


